data.title: Infruset – Själens skrubbsår
data.meta_description: Infruset – Själens skrubbsår with Malmo Symphony Orchestra, Björn Dixgård, Arja Saijonmaa and more, performed in a new setting at the incredible stage Dalhalla, located in Rättvik.
data.text:
Infruset – Själens Skrubbsår was loved by its audiences when it premiered on stage in the grand concert hall, november 2022 – resulting in seven sold out shows. Now, Malmo Live Concert Hall and Geshgore present Infruset – Själens skrubbsår in a new setting: at the beautiful arena Dalhalla in Rättvik, located in the northern parts of Sweden.
